These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
Beverage: cola, hot-chocolate, mirinda, tea
Cigar: bongani, alhambra, montecristo, bluemaster
1. Beverage:hot-chocolate is between Beverage:cola and Cigar:alhambra##2
2. Beverage:hot-chocolate is on the left or right of Cigar:bongani##3
3. Beverage:hot-chocolate is somewhere between Beverage:tea and Beverage:cola##7
4. Cigar:alhambra is in an even position##4
5. Beverage:tea is on the right of Cigar:montecristo##1
6. Cigar:alhambra is somewhere to the left of Cigar:bongani##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | mirinda | tea       | hot-chocolate | cola        |
| Cigar      | montecristo  | alhambra | bluemaster        | bongani |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
Pet: dog, goat, hedgehog, snake
Food: mango, raspberry, peas, pumpkin
1. Food:pumpkin is somewhere between Food:peas and Pet:hedgehog##7
2. Pet:snake is somewhere to the left of Pet:dog##5
3. Pet:snake is somewhere to the right of Food:pumpkin##5
4. Pet:goat is on the left of Pet:snake##1
5. Food:pumpkin is between Food:peas and Food:raspberry##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Pet     | hedgehog | goat       | snake         | dog     |
| Food   | raspberry   | pumpkin | peas | mango |

