3. Hobby:woodworking == Color:green##1
4. Color:red is on the left of Color:green##1
5. Hobby:traveling is on the left of Color:purple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Hobby   | traveling | collecting | writing       | woodworking |
