Pet: dog, mouse, rat, snake
1. Transport:tram is somewhere between Transport:van and Pet:snake##7
2. Transport:quad-bike != Pet:rat##6
3. Pet:mouse != Transport:ship##6
4. Transport:ship is somewhere to the right of Pet:snake##5
5. Transport:van == Pet:dog##1
6. Transport:tram is somewhere to the right of Pet:dog##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Transport   | van | tram | quad-bike | ship |
| Pet           | dog    | mouse   | snake  | rat      |

